{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eva Grinston.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "E-V-A G-R-I-N-S-T-O-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eva Silberstein, which spells S-I-L-B-E-R-S-T-E-I-N.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In I think 1946 or '47, my name was altered by deed poll, and so was my surviving family's name, to Silvan, S-I-L-V-A-N.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fifth of the ninth, 1929.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "66.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-R-A-T-I-S-L-A-V-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My recollections start, I think, at approximately age five-- four, five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a very happy childhood, a sunny childhood I think, in more ways than one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I lived in a very lovely environment, in a very attractive house, which belonged to my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was an added joy to my childhood that my grandparents lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were above them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had a-- a very close connection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have to correct this now, because I never knew my grandfather, only my grandmother, who lived, as I say, below our home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our house was surrounded by a very nice garden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister, Vera, who was two years younger than I-- barely two years-- and I spent a lot of our time, in fact, in that garden, which was big enough for us to have private corners and very, very precious places for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had very caring parents, a very devoted, dedicated mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandmother lived with two maiden aunts, her daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, they were spoiling me and behaving in a wonderful fashion to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My constant companion, apart from my mother, was a fraulein, who looked after me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think she was there from as long as I can remember, to the very period when we could no longer afford to have her, which might have been at age six.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can only tell you-- I thank you for that comment.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
